Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF MACAUCANG MUNICIPALITY OF NAUJAN, PROVINCE OF MINDORO, TO THAT OF AURORA.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 573, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF MACAUCANG MUNICIPALITY OF NAUJAN, PROVINCE OF MINDORO, TO THAT OF AURORA.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Macaucang, of the municipality of Naujan, Province of Mindoro, is changed to that of Aurora.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.ℒαwρhi৷
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 8, 1940.
